Title: An Act Changing the Name of the City of Roxas High School in the City of Roxas to Congressman Ramon A. Arnaldo High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 332
An Act Changing the Name of the City of Roxas High School in the City of Roxas to Congressman Ramon A. Arnaldo High School
Section 1. The name of the City of Roxas High School in the City of Roxas is changed to Congressman Ramon A. Arnaldo High School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 19, 1983
